      • computeNeedsPatching

        protected void computeNeedsPatching()
        Computes boxToNeedsPatching which maps each UnitBox from a PhiExpr to true if the referenced Unit falls-through to the statement containing the PhiExpr, false otherwise. NOTE: This will *miss* all the Phi nodes outside a chain. So make sure you know what you are doing if you remove a Phi node from a chain and don't put it back or call clearUnitBoxes() on it.
